865
01:23:29.041 --> 01:23:31.540
It's only fair you
do the same to him.

866
01:23:31.541 --> 01:23:32.457
No.

867
01:23:32.458 --> 01:23:34.791
No.

868
01:23:42.666 --> 01:23:43.666
Yeah.

869
01:23:53.291 --> 01:23:54.207
No.

870
01:23:54.208 --> 01:23:56.874
No! No. please
don't! It's a lie!

871
