Take care of her.

915
01:28:29.625 --> 01:28:31.207
I will. Dad. I will.

916
01:28:31.208 --> 01:28:32.500
Take care of her.

917
01:28:33.583 --> 01:28:34.708
Take care of her.

918
01:28:38.958 --> 01:28:39.958
Dad?

919
01:28:42.708 --> 01:28:43.708
Dad?

920
01:28:45.125 --> 01:28:46.125
Dad.

921
